itm_name: 567 PCS Cake Decorating Kit Baking Supplies with 3 Springform Pans Set, Cake Decorating Supplies Rotating Turntable, Decorating Tools, Cake Baking Supplies Set for Beginners and Cake Lovers
itm_dsc:
567 PCS Cake Decorating Kit Cake Making Kit, the Sweet Maker!

What's including in the cake kit?

  • 1 cake decorating turntable, 1 cake levler, 1 chocolate mold, 8 flour flag, 1 Egg Beaters,1 Ciong Coupers, 1 Cream Scraper, 1 Straigh Spatul, 1 Angled Spatula, 1 cake Server, 1 Cake knife, 1 Cake Smoother, 1 Cake Board, 1 flour sieve, 60 baking papers(7/9 ), 1 Scrapper Sets, 1 Flower Nail, 1 Lifter, 1 Brush, 1 chart
  • 2 Silicone Bags, 2 Russian Tricoupers, 3 PCS leakproof cake Pans(4/7/9 inch),6 Muffin Cup Molds, 7 Russian tips, 8 flags, 9 Carved Pens,
  • 24PCS Numbered Icing tips, 50 Muffin Cups, 50 plags, 100PCS Disposable Bags, 200PCS Paper Cupcakes
  • Complete cake kits for any cake you make!

Baking Cake Process of Non-Stick Springform Pans

Here are the suggestion temperature and time for different Springform Pans (only for ChIFFON CAKE)

9 inch : 150 ℃ ( 302 ℉ ) - 50-80 Minutes

7 inch : 150 ℃ ( 302 ℉ )- 40-60 Minutes

4 inch: 150 ℃( 302 ℉ ) - 20-30 Minutes

You can adjust the temperature and baking time according to your taste

All Springform Pans is easy to release with release latch, and removable smooth bottom.

After baking, it's better to release after cool.

After using, it's better to soak, then wash.

Good cake set for making cakes and cake decorating class

NOTE： There is non-stick coating on the springform pans, please don't use hard washing brush to wash them.

8 PCS Happy Birthday Flags

We include 8 PCS different styles happy birthday flags to match your custom cakes, You can use these baking decorating supplies when making a birthday cake.

Installation Process

Here are the installation process of the silicone bags, it’s same as the disposable bags. Easy and fast.

Installation Process

Here are the installation process of the silicone bags, it’s same as the disposable bags. Easy and fast.

cake piping kit

You can ues of these cake piping kit to custom and decorate the various cakes, It's also an essential tool in baking sets.

Customised decoration of your cake

You can custom and decorate various cakes with all cake decorating kits in cake decorating class.

Cake Leveler

The cake leveler is designed to help professional cake makers and hobbyists to ensure that each layer is flat, parallel and of the same size when creating multi-tier cakes.
